description:
Service under this Rate Schedule is available throughout the Cooperative's service area in accordance with the Cooperative's established Rules and Regulations for Electric Service.  Service Hereunder is limited to Consumers who require an annual peak demand of at least 1,000 kW, and an annual load factor of at least 60%. In order to receive service under this rate, Consumers will be required to sign an electric service contract with a minimum initial term of three (3) years and requiring a minimum of thirty (30) days advance notice to cancel thereafter.

The Standard Demand Charge will be reduced based upon the Consumer's load factor over the previous 12 billing months. as follows:

               Load Factor                           Standard Demand Charge
              Less than 60%                                 $6.85 per kW
              At least 60% but less than 70%                $6.15 per kW
              At least 70 % but less than 80%               $5.80 per kW
              80% and above                                 $5.50 per kW
